    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specimen, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a robust Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the 333 hp output with factory precision. A mechanically sorted, driver-spec icon that delivers unfiltered analog feedback and exceptional longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
